    "title": "京东开放平台发布违禁商品及信息管理规范-通讯、上网、无线电类设备类实施细则",
    "followRuleId": "1241923649624215552",
    "content": "<p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 等线; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #333333;\">京东开放平台发布违禁商品及信息管理规范</span>中对应章节标准：</span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.13</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">通讯、上网、无线电类设备类：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.13.1</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">破网、翻墙软件及VPN代理服务</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">背景：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">根据《中华人民共和国网络安全法》、《计算机信息网络国际联网管理暂行规定》、《电信业务经营许可管理办法》等法规，提供国际通信业务或跨境网络接入服务属于增值电信业务，必须取得国家电信主管部门的许可。任何组织或个人不得擅自建立或使用非法信道进行国际联网。请遵守相关法律法规的规定。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规则定义：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">破网、翻墙的软件、服务及相关教程；所有VPN产品，包括账号、服务器、软件、卡密及变相的网络加速器等；收看境外节目的软件或服务；境外平台账号相关的商品及服务；修改IP地址的软件，包括但不限于秒拨（混拨）IP服务器，混拨VPS拨号服务器。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">标准：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①严禁发布任何用于破网、翻墙的软件、工具、教程；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">②严禁提供境外账号注册服务；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">③不得发布任何可用于修改IP地址的软件内容；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 26px; font-family: 等线; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px; color: #262626;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; margin: inherit; padding: inherit;\">④禁止发布&ldquo;翻墙&rdquo;服务、传播&ldquo;翻墙&rdquo;教程、推广&ldquo;翻墙&rdquo;工具和&ldquo;翻墙&rdquo;各类广告信息；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 26px; font-family: 等线; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px; color: #262626;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; margin: inherit; padding: inherit;\">⑤禁止发布宣介、提供&ldquo;代装可调用境外在封大模型的OpenClaw服务&rdquo;&ldquo;提供境外在封大模型调用服务&rdquo;教授使用方法等相关商品；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 26px; font-family: 等线; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px; color: #262626;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; margin: inherit; padding: inherit;\">⑥禁止发布可调用或接入境外在封大模型（包括gemini、sora、claude、chatgpt、nano banana、grok、MiniMax）等相关商品及禁止发布相关软件会员激活代充等服务。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">温馨提示：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">无代理服务的硬件、VPN相关正规出版书籍可以发布。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">常见问题：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">什么是翻墙软件？</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">翻墙软件是指通过代理链接访问境外网站的软件。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.13.2</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">卫星信号收发装置及软件；用于无线电信号屏蔽的仪器或设备</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规则背景：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">请遵守相关法律法规的规定。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规则定义：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">卫星电视地面接收设施及配件，包括卫星锅、高频头、接收机、黑卡、编码器、解码器、解压及接收一体装置、服务(费）、账号等；商品信息中明确表示或暗示可以收看境外电视台或港澳台地区的电视台或黄色内容的电视棒、网络播放器；数字电视破解卡；具有屏蔽、阻断、干扰手机信号或者GPS信号等功能的屏蔽器类商品。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">案例：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border-style: none; word-break: break-all;\" src=\"https://img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/327619/13/11931/258794/68aeed2dF68e1c678/ab7e83fcd48e463b.png\" width=\"400\" /></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">温馨提示：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商品信息中涉及任何非法描述、诱导客户做不道德行为，或者写明&ldquo;请勿用于非法用途&rdquo;的商品，都不可以发布。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">常见问题：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">电视棒可以出售吗？</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">不可以，其他电视卡类商品标题、描述、主图等商品信息中也不可以出现&ldquo;电视棒&rdquo;等描述。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">数字电视破解卡可以出售吗？</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">不可以，通过标题、图片或是描述中任一处可判定商品为利用非法手段免费收看数字电视的数字电视破解卡类商品，都不可以发布。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.13.3</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">已激活的手机卡、上网卡等违反国家规定的商品</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规则背景：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">请遵守相关法律法规的规定。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规则定义：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">激活过的手机卡、固定电话号码、流量卡等；物联网卡；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">常见问题：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">激活过是指什么？</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">激活过指需要实名登记信息的号卡在销售之前已经被他人注册但未注销的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">入网是指什么？</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">入网是指用户办理固定电话装机、移机、过户，移动电话开户、过户等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">IP</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">卡属于禁售范围吗？</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">IP</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">卡暂不属于禁售范围。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">什么是物联网卡？</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">物联网卡是运营商为物流网服务企业提供的用于智能终端设备联网的，仅面对企业用户进行批量销售，广泛用于共享单车、移动支付、智能城市、自动售卖机等领域，不面向个人用户。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">附则：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家的行为，发生在本规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东可根据运营情况随时调整本规则并以公告的形式向商家公示。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有约定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无约定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议；若商家服务协议约定的违约金金额高于规则约定的，京东有权适用协议约定。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本规则于2026年5月27日修订，于2026年6月3日生效。</span></span></p>",
